channel.description:
[center][img]http://i56.tinypic.com/svgtn8.jpg[/img]
Server Base: Pi released by Moe Client Base: Galkons refactored (currently at the 317 revision of runescape if a client developer applies and wants to upgrade it will be allowed.)
The color red will represent not started. The color orange will represent not started. The color green will represent completed.
[u][b]Combat[/b][/u]
[IMG]http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110305042726/runescape/images/5/51/Attack-icon.png[/img]Melee Clipping Special Attacks Max Hits Correct Bonuses Attack Speeds Correct Animations Correct Effects Attack Styles Weapon Timers
[img]http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110305043125/runescape/images/7/77/Magic-icon.png[/img]Magic Projectiles Autocasting Correct Animations Hit Delays Autocasting Splashing Correct Effects Correct distance and magic following Correct Animations Perfect Combat Formula Correct Distance Magic Following Delays
[img]http://images3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110305043145/runescape/images/7/72/Ranged-icon.png[/img]Range Projectiles Special Attacks Projectiles Correct Bonuses Correct Arrows Max hits Attack Speeds Correct Animations Correct Effects Delays
[img]http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20091215022527/runescape/images/2/24/Prayer-icon.png[/img]Prayer Normal prayers. Bones on altar
[u][b]Skills[/b][/u]
[img]http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20091205044857/runescape/images/2/28/Mining-icon.png[/img]Mining Support all pickaxes Support all ores Prospecting Correct animations
[img]http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20091205043729/runescape/images/0/0b/Fishing-icon.png[/img]Fishing Support all fishes Correct timers Correct equipment Correct animations
[img]http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20091205043729/runescape/images/0/0b/Fishing-icon.png[/img]Cooking All fishes to be cooked Able to cook on ranges Cook on open fires Correct interfaces, and animations Correct timers
[img]http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20091231200718/runescape/images/0/0f/Woodcutting-icon.png[/img]Woodcutting Support all trees Support all axes Create stumps (using events) Correct animations Level requirements
[img]http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20101104013322/runescape/images/8/84/Agility-icon.png[/img]Agility Correct delays and timers Gnome course
[img]http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20091231200718/runescape/images/f/f3/Thieving-icon.png[/img]Thieving All stalls work Pickpocket NPCs Correct animations Stalls dissapearing (using events)
[img]http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20091231200717/runescape/images/7/77/Fletching-icon.png[/img]Fletching Support all logs Correct delays and timers Correct requirements
[img]http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20091205043729/runescape/images/6/6d/Firemaking-icon.png[/img]Firemaking Support all logs Projectiles Non-supported areas Correct delays and timers
[img]http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20101103053740/runescape/images/6/64/Runecrafting-icon.png[/img]Runecrafting Support all runes All tiaras
[img]http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20101103032422/runescape/images/c/cf/Slayer-icon.png[/img]Slayer Slayer Tower Slayer tasks with rewards Slayer gem Correct dialogues Tasks based of combat level
*Note* Skills not here are not planned on being added yet.*
[b][u]Minigames[/u][/b]
Duel Arena Tzhaar Caves Castle Wars Pest Control Barrows Fight Pits Warriors Guild
[b][u]Bosses[/u][/b]
King Black Dragon Kalphite Queen Chaos Elemental Dagannoth Kings
[b][u]Miscellaneous[/u][/b]
Quests All known Dupes Fixed Clipped Following Clipped Npcs Teletabs Good combat Good switching[/center]
Ill be posting open spots tomorrow and also adding media tomorrow. If you want more information shoot me a pm.
